  <brief_title>Incidence and Patterns of Nausea/Vomiting With Combined Chemotherapy and Radiation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Study to Evaluate the Incidence and Patterns of Nausea and Vomiting in Patients Receiving Combined Chemotherapy and Radiation</official_title>
