  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Questionnaire study to observe the incidence and pattern or nausea and vomiting in patients
      receiving combined chemotherapy and radiation. 83% of patients experience radiation
      therapy-induced vomiting; significant nausea and vomiting could develop with concurrent
      chemotherapy despite standard anti-nauseous medication prophylaxis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Questionnaires will be answered daily on a weekly basis during period of radiation and
      chemotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
